# EchoForgeDelta â€“ Log Diff & Insight Extractor

EchoForgeDelta finds differences in logs between two time windows or versions, helping diagnose regressions and config drifts.

## Features
- Log diffing by message, timestamp, or pattern
- Environment-to-environment comparison
- Markdown and HTML report output

